-- Saudi Arabia's Alinma Bank plans 2014 dividend of 5 riyals
-- 
-- Thu Dec 25, 2014 03:24AM EST
-- None



DUBAI, Dec 25 (Reuters) - The board of Saudi Arabia's Alinma Bank <1150.SE> said on Thursday that it was recommending a dividend of 5.0 riyals per share for 2014.

It would be the bank's first dividend since it listed on the stock market in 2008.